data.description: This is a great Larger Townhome with a very open floorplan. Newly installed AC will keep you comfortable in the heat of summer. Large master bedroom with a walk-in closet and 5pc master bathroom.  2 other good size bedrooms and another full bathroom complete the upper level. Close to Ft Carson and Peterson/Shriver AFB.  Shopping and entertainment are near by as well as all the outdoor activities.
